{"id":1705,"date":"2021-09-01T15:21:20","date_gmt":"2021-09-01T15:21:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/?p=1705"},"modified":"2021-09-02T11:26:34","modified_gmt":"2021-09-02T11:26:34","slug":"live-update-01-09-2021","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/2021\/09\/01\/live-update-01-09-2021\/","title":{"rendered":"Live Update 01\/09\/2021"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Please note that the <strong>information below is not final<\/strong>, and certain aspects may be <strong>subject to change<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>CONTENTS<\/strong>:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Alliance War &#8211; The Thirteenth Labor &#8211; Heracles<ol><li>Relic Overview<\/li><li>Milestone Rewards<\/li><li>Alliance Rewards<\/li><li>Chosen Titans and Boost Relic<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>DoT Content Creators<\/li><li>Unofficial Social Channels<\/li><li>Official Social Channels<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>ALLIANCE WAR &#8211; <\/strong><strong><em>The Thirteenth Labor &#8211; Heracles<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/vCc96DQLl2p9c15TLZDbd73BYrL7ENSgdgVumekm5jetH6K3JoyW39Wf4DGMrONKSIkbWQ8EvAqhn-gc41S--RWal7SUHiXW0bzBcYm8hLciTKlsjnx9slUMv7tAaV99yBANMcZw=s0\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>STARTS:<\/strong> 2nd September, 15:00 UTC<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>ENDS:<\/strong> 6th September, 09:00 UTC<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>While the battle had fallen silent for several days, the earth of the battlefield continued to smoulder and fill the air with the foul stench of death. Everdure cautiously stepped over the fallen as he approached the nucleus of the site. There, in a pile of charred bone and steel, Everdure picked up the <\/em><strong><em>Divine Geode<\/em><\/strong><em>.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>\u2018So, it was left here after all\u2026\u2019 Everdure mused. \u2018The path forward is clear. We must call a great council\u2019<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Previously sworn rivals, the call of the council was great enough to summon leaders from every faction, from Asgard and Egypt to the Ragnar and Mossmane tribes. Seated at the great <\/em><strong><em>Roundtable of Zalon<\/em><\/strong><em>, Everdure explained that with the Geode he would have the power to open a portal into the realm of the <\/em><strong><em>Nexus<\/em><\/strong><em>, where one hero could venture through and end the threat once and for all.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Erupting in shouts and exclamations, every faction desired to claim this honour for themselves. Even Korthan, the King of the Human kingdoms, declared that the honour should fall to him. For it was his sword, <\/em><strong><em>Excalibur<\/em><\/strong><em>, that clashed with Almarand\u2019s and started the cataclysm and set the Nexus energies loose upon the Shattered Kingdoms.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>\u2018SILENCE\u2019 Everdure cried. \u2018While your enthusiasm is welcomed, my Lords and Ladies, I fear that our choice is somewhat pre-determined.\u2019&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Everdure went on to explain that the Nexus energies on the other side of the portal were too powerful for any human to withstand. Any hero who ventured through would likely meet the same fate as Almarand, and end up a puppet of the Nexus. On the other hand, Everdure\u2019s power even with the Divine Geode was not strong enough to send through a God of Olympus or Asgard without risk of alerting the Nexus forces.&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>\u2018This peril will require a very special type of hero, someone who can pass through the portal, but will not succumb to the vile will of the Nexus\u2019 Everdure warned<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>With that, Gaia stood up and motioned to Heracles who stepped forward and knelt before the all-mother.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>\u2018It falls upon you, my child. Not fully a God, or fully a man &#8211; your spirit will be able to withstand the corruption and you may venture where we cannot.\u2019 Gaia whispered. \u2018Rise, HERACLES, and venture forth. Our fate rests in your hands\u2019<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>\u2018Aye.\u2019 Korthan joined \u2018Here, my lad, take this sword. It\u2019s history is great, but it\u2019s power is greater. There is no hero more worthy to wield it than you.\u2019<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>With that the council erupted in a roar of cheers. Heracles gripped <\/em><strong><em>Excalibur<\/em><\/strong><em>, looked to Everdure, and nodded that he was ready.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1014\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Heracles-1024x1014.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Heracles-1024x1014.png 1024w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Heracles-300x297.png 300w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Heracles-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Heracles-768x760.png 768w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Heracles.png 1097w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Heracles, reborn as a mighty 4\u2605 Paladin, makes his debut to the Shattered Kingdoms this Thursday 2nd of September.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Knossos Bulls<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Heracles, Demigod and Champion of Olympus, unleashes the raging Knossos Bulls and seeks to restore Peace to the Shattered Kingdoms by any means necessary.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/knossos.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1708\" width=\"383\" height=\"737\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/knossos.png 511w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/knossos-156x300.png 156w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 383px) 100vw, 383px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Get these<strong> powerful Relics and more <\/strong>in the Milestone Rewards:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"952\" height=\"680\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/heracles_relics222.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1716\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/heracles_relics222.png 952w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/heracles_relics222-300x214.png 300w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/heracles_relics222-768x549.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 952px) 100vw, 952px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"948\" height=\"679\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/heracles_relics2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1710\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/heracles_relics2.png 948w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/heracles_relics2-300x215.png 300w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/heracles_relics2-768x550.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 948px) 100vw, 948px\" \/